new file mode 100644
index 00000000..dd7a22ff
--- /dev/null
+++ b/packaging/homebrew/README.md
@@ -0,0 +1,13 @@
+# Homebrew tap package
+
+The release workflow renders `hive.rb.erb` exclusively from canonical
+`release.json`, then dispatches the version and arm64 checksum to
+`ivankuznetsov/homebrew-hive`. Users install with:
+
+```bash
+brew install ivankuznetsov/hive/hive
+```
+
+The formula contains no Ruby runtime dependency; its binary already embeds
+Ruby. Daemon registration remains an explicit `hive init` or
+`hive daemon service install` decision.
